Package proguard.classfile.util

Class PrimitiveArrayConstantReplacer

  • java.lang.Object
    • proguard.classfile.util.PrimitiveArrayConstantReplacer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeVisitor, ConstantVisitor, PrimitiveArrayConstantElementVisitor, InstructionVisitor, ClassVisitor
    public class PrimitiveArrayConstantReplacer
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClassVisitor, AttributeVisitor, InstructionVisitor, ConstantVisitor, PrimitiveArrayConstantElementVisitor
    This ClassVisitor replaces all instances of PrimitiveArrayConstant by Java bytecode compliant array store instructions.
    See Also:
    ArrayInitializationReplacer
